getDismissType

public DismissType getDismissType()
Returns:
- Whether or not the in-app message should automatically dismiss itself, or if the user should be required to swipe it away. Note: swipe functionality is only available for API versions 12 (Android 3.1) and up. For older versions of Android, the dismiss type will always be DismissType.AUTO_DISMISS.

createSlideup

public static Slideup createSlideup(java.lang.String message,
                                    SlideFrom slideFrom,
                                    DismissType dismissType,
                                    int durationInMilliseconds)
Convenience method to create Slideup objects.

Parameters:
message - The slideup message.
slideFrom - The direction from which the slideup will be displayed.
dismissType - The way in which to dismiss the slideup.
durationInMilliseconds - The amount of time to display the slideup if the dismiss type is DismissType.AUTO.
Returns:
A newly constructed slideup.
